056.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tesla-directors-agree-to-return-735-million-following-claims-they-were-massively-overpaid-105506056.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 258a76e3-16b1-49a9-bca7-d55733772d5a</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jul 2023 10:55:06 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689674115</ingested><modified> 2023-07-18T09:55:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1920" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/095902a0-254a-11ee-baff-a734193e8db3" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1920" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/095902a0-254a-11ee-baff-a734193e8db3" width="3000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - A sign marks the entrance to the Tesla Gigafactory, Oct. 13, 2018, in Sparks, Nev. Tesla will get more than $330 million in tax breaks from Nevada to massively expand its vehicle battery facility east of Reno and add a new electric semi-truck factory. Approval on Thursday, March 2, 2023, from the Governor's Office of Economic Development came as Republican Gov. Joe Lombardo cited the benefit of jobs and the boost that Tesla's huge Gigafactory has given the local economy for almost a decade. (AP Photo/John Locher, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Tesla Expansion Nevada Taxes]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tesla's 'Charge on Solar' lets Powerwall owners send excess energy to their EV]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/teslas-texas-factory-has-produced-its-first-cybertruck-161840934.html">特斯拉</a>推出了一项名为“<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.tesla.com/support/tesla-app/charge-on-solar">太阳能充电</a>”的功能，允许车主仅使用多余的太阳能来为电动汽车的电池充电。正如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/07/17/tesla-lets-owners-recharge-with-solar/"><em>TechCrunch</em></a>指出的那样，该汽车制造商于 5 月份开始测试该功能，但现在它已更广泛地提供给美国和加拿大的特斯拉客户。然而，可以访问该功能的人数可能仍然非常有限。首先，只有那些拥有较新特斯拉（2021 年及以后）并且还拥有 Powerwall 的人才能使用它。这是该公司的电池系统，用于存储太阳能电池板利用的太阳能。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/db445110-2546-11ee-affe-bd8d5e67861e" style="height:1051px;width:1536px;" alt="特斯拉新太阳能充电功能的屏幕截图。" data-uuid="90a24675-5ddd-308d-975b-681f6dd502d7"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">特斯拉</div></figure><p>要启用太阳能充电，用户需要启动特斯拉应用程序，选择该功能，然后进行设置。然后，他们会在功能设置中看到一个带有太阳图标的滑块，他们可以向左或向右拖动该滑块来设置充电限制。在到达太阳滑块之前，车辆将像往常一样通过太阳能和电网自行充电，确保用户有足够的电力到达他们需要的地方。但到达太阳滑块后，车辆只会使用多余的太阳能为自己充电。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>当处于风暴监视模式时，Powerwall 仍会优先存储备用能源或为其他设备充电，然后再分配任何多余的太阳能用于车辆充电。太阳能充电实际上只会使用多余的能量为电动汽车充电，这也是为什么担心电量不足的车主可以为其设置时间限制。当然，如果他们想绝对确保电池充满电，他们也可以调整充电限制，或者完全关闭太阳能充电。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/teslas-charge-on-solar-lets-powerwall-owners-send-excess-energy-to-their-ev-102018496.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/teslas-charge-on-solar-lets-powerwall-owners-send-excess-energy-to-their-ev-102018496.html?src=rs